+    max_price: OpenEye addition — Facebook's `maxPrice` filter. Pass 0 to sweep for
+    FREE items only (e.g. a free RTX 4090 / Aeron). Omitted -> no price ceiling.
+
+    radius_km / latitude / longitude: OpenEye addition — best-effort geographic widening.
+    Facebook honors radius most reliably when an explicit lat/long is supplied alongside it;
+    with only the city slug it may ignore radius. No harm if ignored — the slug still works.
+    """
     encoded_query = quote(query)
     url = f"https://www.facebook.com/marketplace/{location_id}/search?query={encoded_query}&locale={locale}"
     if days_listed is not None:
         url += f"&daysSinceListed={days_listed}"
+    if max_price is not None:
